---
title: Pork and Charred Corn Chimichurri Tacos with Lime Crema and Tomato
description: In this delicious mash-up, sweet-and-smoky charred corn is tossed with bright, herbaceous cilantro chimichurri to create the most surprising (and not to mention delicious) salsa. It’s piled into steamy tortillas along with saucy spiced pork, a tangle of veggies, a dollop of lime crema, and a sprinkling of chopped chili. It’s always Tuesday in our hearts!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/2019-w17-r17-pork-and-charred-corn-chimichurri-tacos-34d259e2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/2019-w17-r17-pork-and-charred-corn-chimichurri-tacos-5c82a9a4c445fa1e573a9382-01faf625.pdf
